  handleTrailer=(movie)=>{
    this.setState({
      selectedmovie:movie
    })
  } 

  render() {
    const  {movie,selectedmovie}=this.state;
   const movielist= Object.keys(movie).map((list, index)=> {
      if(selectedmovie===index)
      {
        return(
          <div  key={movie[list].EventTitle} className=" col-xs-6 col-sm-4 col-md-3 card active-card">
          <div onClick={()=>this.handleTrailer(index)} className="card-content">
          {/* {movie[list].EventTitle} */}
        <img src={`https://in.bmscdn.com/events/moviecard/${movie[list].EventCode}.jpg`}/>
          </div>
          <Videoplayer src={movie[list].TrailerURL}/>
          </div>
        )
      }
      else{
        return(
          <div  key={movie[list].EventTitle} className=" col-xs-6 col-sm-4 col-md-3 card">
          <div onClick={()=>this.handleTrailer(index)} className="card-content">
          {/* {movie[list].EventTitle} */}
          <img src={`https://in.bmscdn.com/events/moviecard/${movie[list].EventCode}.jpg`}/>

          </div>
          </div>
        )
      }    
    });
    // const movielist=movie.map((list,index)=>{

    // })
    return (
      <div   className="App  container">
      <div className="row">
      {movielist}
      </div>
      </div>
    );
  }
